{"title": "Three tips to avoid buying unsuitable investment products", "tags": "business", "timestamp": "2024-07-06", "content": "SINGAPORE \u2013 If you are looking for fixed-income returns, you should deal with only reputable parties that are financially stable, otherwise you could end up losing all your money.\nAfter all, your funds are only as safe as the companies that offer them. As seasoned investors will tell you, even listed companies and international banks can be in trouble when the global economy tanks."}